<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-20T17:21:02-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-20T17:21:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-20T17:21:02-04:00</updated><title> Cards Against Humanity 起诉 SpaceX 侵犯其“原始”财产</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;埃隆·马斯克的照片拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dUE5f6RLr4QsS2-wxDCsnRRw28M=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73599753/STK022_ELON_MUSK_CVIRGINIA_C.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge |摄影：STR / NurPhoto、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;K2zd6X&quot;>;反人类卡牌组织起诉 SpaceX，称其涉嫌侵入并损坏其在德克萨斯州的财产。根据其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/25169455-cards-against- humanity-v-spacex-elon-musk? responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;针对 SpaceX 的投诉&lt;/a>;，于周四向德克萨斯州法院提起，但&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cahsuesmusk.com/&quot;>;还表示&lt;/a>;它将“接受 Twitter.com 作为补偿”。诉讼称，SpaceX 在未经许可的情况下使用德克萨斯州卡梅伦县的“原始空置财产”已有大约六个月的时间。卡牌反人类组织 (Cards Against Humanity) 于 2017 年购买了该地块，作为“让[前总统唐纳德]特朗普建造隔离墙尽可能耗时且昂贵”的噱头的一部分。此后，SpaceX 收购了反人类卡片组织财产周围道路上的“许多空地”，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/20 /24250269/cards-against-Humanity-space-x-lawsuit-cameron-county-texas&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/20/24250269/cards-against-humanity-space-x-lawsuit-cameron-county-texas" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/20/24250269/cards-against- humanity-space-x-lawsuit-cameron-county-texas</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-20T16:57:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-20T16:57:54-04:00</updated><title>最好的扫地机器人</title><c